都要比人斬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下撞掉你部電話</blockquote><br />\n...你不如話試下被人撞落路軌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下撞死你老母</blockquote><br />\n睇住伯友呀，一陣伯友搭火車一個唔覺意被人撞一下就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cba4587bd949eae2009ba4983ed1ed080e5eba0b","tid":334924,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:44:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>比人打都唔還拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃圾<br />\n起碼都伸佢一腳先啦<br />\n<br />\n利申 隻腳有c朗咁粗 一腳應該可以收佢皮</blockquote><br />\n還左就會比人告埋一份。香港係咁。</blockquote><br />\n其實案中疑犯平日係連登就好似依位巴打咁<br />\n疑犯：俾人撞親都唔還拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃圾<br />\n起碼都撞到佢仆街啦</blockquote><br />\n無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通好似你咁衝住拎個老母出黎比人屌仲笑笑口咁大方咩</blockquote><br />\n痴撚線 下下拎老母出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老母唔屌 屌邊個呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我屌你老母我條野又唔係你老母個度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11fc0860dd2615d7ba5fd3a7825f412d2d7aa124","tid":334924,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:46:15.000Z","msg":"睇下撞到咩程度啦， 大大力撞當然要道歉啦<br />\n比我都嬲"},{"pid":"1b7fcda754f33e622728e7cd56fa88b64bcdcd15","tid":334924,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:49:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好心人幫人捱左幾刀只換黎一句&quot;佢幾好人&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></block